Package us.aaronweiss.juicebot

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Client
    A basic abstraction for all IRC clients.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoBot
    A basic bot that auto-rejoins upon being kicked, and attempts to avert poor bans.
    Bot
    The core of all juicebot bots, handling all necessary internals.
    DataAwareBot
    A bot with embedded access to the information API.
    ManagedBot
    An AutoBot with a built-in owner.
    Message
    An immutable received message over IRC.
    MessageBot
    A Bot using the POJO Messaging API.
    SessionData
    The core data element for the Information API.
    SimpleBot
    A Bot using the Simple String Array Messaging API.
  • Enum Summary

    An enumeration of server response codes based on RFC 1459.
